  <summary date="2022-01-04T14:34:37Z" status="Introduced in House">Building Our Opportunities to Survive and Thrive Act of 2021 or the BOOST Act of 2021

This bill allows certain individual taxpayers a refundable income-based tax credit equal to $3,000 in a taxable year. It also directs the Internal Revenue Service to establish a program for making advance payments of such credit on a monthly basis.</summary>
